    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (wp.exp((v2 + 0.22 / v2 + 0.76)) / wp.exp((v1 + 0.47 + v1 + 0.80)))
    tmp = wp.sin(0.17)
    v2 = ((wp.sin(v1 + 0.33) - (v2 + 0.18 - v1 + 0.70)) * (wp.exp(v2 + 0.41) * (v1 + 0.55 * v0 + 0.01)))
